data.description: Stunning Henderson residence near Chimera Golf Club! This Henderson home boasts a captivating open floorplan accentuated by expansive windows adorned with elegant shutters. Bamboo, upgraded carpet, & tile flooring adorn the interiors, adding a touch of sophistication to every corner. The stylish kitchen is a culinary haven featuring a breakfast bar island, sleek stainless steel fixtures, & a convenient walk-in pantry complete with a built-in wine rack. The first floor also features a bedroom & 3/4 bath. Notable amenities include upgraded paint finishes, a thoughtfully designed office nook, an upstairs laundry room with new washer & dryer, & closets equipped with built-in shelving & a safe. Outdoor living in the backyard is enhanced by a shaded patio, perfect for relaxation & entertaining alike.
